explanation.summary: Kt qu phn tch in tim cho thy nhp tim ca bn chm hn mc bnh thng (Nhp chm).
explanation.details: Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy cc nhp p cch xa nhau, nhng u n, vi hnh dng sng QRS bnh thng. Nhp tim hin ti l 53.42 ln/pht, thp hn mc chun thng thng l 60-100 ln/pht. Tuy nhin, thi gian dn truyn in tim (QRS 0.112s) vn nm trong gii hn bnh thng, cho thy ng dn truyn in trong cc bung tim di hot ng n nh v khng c du hiu bt thng nghim trng. iu ny c ngha l mc d tim p chm, nhng cch thc dn truyn in ca tim vn din ra theo mt quy trnh bnh thng.
explanation.recommendations: Nhp tim chm c th l mt tnh trng bnh thng  mt s ngi khe mnh, c bit l cc vn ng vin chuyn nghip. Tuy nhin, nu bn cm thy mt mi, chng mt, kh th, au ngc hoc c bt k triu chng no khc, bn cn thng bo ngay cho bc s. Trnh cc yu t c th lm chm nhp tim thm nu bn khng chc chn v nguyn nhn.
